In large resealable plastic bag, pour Lawry's(R) Thai Ginger Marinade With Lime Juice over beef; turn to coat. Close bag and marinate in refrigerator 30 minutes. Remove beef from Marinade, discarding Marinade. Meanwhile, in medium bowl, combine mango, red pepper, carrot and jalapeno pepper; set aside. In 12-inch skillet, heat oil over medium-high heat and cook beef, stirring occasionally, 5 minutes. Evenly spoon beef into lettuce leaves, then top with mango mixture; roll up.